{"tid":955254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社區組織協會促港府向內地單親家庭單程證","createTime":"2018-12-25T08:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T09:24:04.000Z","uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bccf93bd4e253f6f4c1c54f9a35959f23b5e9c42","tid":955254,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:59:25.000Z","msg":"團體促港府向內地爭取單親家庭單程證<br />\n3小時前  Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】有團體趁聖誕遊行，促請特區政府向內地爭取單親家庭單程證配額。<br />\n<br />\n社區組織協會與中港分離單親家庭關注會約30名兒童及單親家長，戴起聖誕帽及手持標語，由中環皇后像廣場遊行到禮賓府。<br />\n<br />\n他們促請政府與內地當局檢視現時單程證，要求容許單親家庭申請，又指現時每日150個單程證名額未用盡，應該利用這些空間，協助單親家庭在港團聚。<br />\n<br />\n組織相信中港單親家庭兒童的成長過程缺乏親人照料，不利他們成長。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=331933&amp;refer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331933%26refer&d=%2Bx%2FO5aMVOz%2Fb6Hk2i1FBc%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=aca08814\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331933%26refer&h=51bd8d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=331933&amp;refer</a>"},{"pid":"d60b6dc174f1f973f7135daa9eb8e86b34276b9e","tid":955254,"uid":64374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c19a5981cbd3dd40ff62d4aa9047cea270441854","tid":955254,"uid":192517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:02:59.000Z","msg":"社區組織協會=民主黨<br />\n<br />\n醒未呀？廿年鳩up民主<br />\n民主姐係市民作主，但係班粉腸多次同市民作對，乜撚野民主呀！<br />\n<br />\n最柒既係d所謂支持者又會扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"0b407a9513621adc0018619d430a6f7c2f80db7e","tid":955254,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"奪回審批權？"},{"pid":"4069144d991497347c1c82ae34be2d67c5bd57f6","tid":955254,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b407a9513621adc0018619d430a6f7c2f80db7e","tid":955254,"uid"